steps.description:
* Turn in Quest, Accept: Indurium, Barbecued Buzzard Wings
* Go south

* Kill Mobs, Loot Quest Item
* GO back to Camp, Turn in Quest / Accept next part
* Go NorthWest; Accept Quest: Study of the Elements: Rock
* Go West ways

* Go Get Flight Point
* Go up the watch tower accept Quests (2)
* Go in the INN, accept Quests (2) (one is Upstairs)
* Go back to EAST, Kill Earth-Elementals (Finish Stone quest)
steps.tips: * DON'T BIND YOURSELF, keep your HS to Grom'Gol

steps.description:
* kill all missing Earth Elementals (Loot items)
* Turn Rock quest in, Accept next part
* Go south Kill Elementals again...
* grind your way back, Kill Coyotes and Buzzards (do not finish now)
* Turn in quest, Accept next part

* Look for Boss Tho'grun (BLUE), kill and loot
* Kill All missing Buzzards (Loot items Gizzard + Wings) (RED B)
* Kill Elementals (RED E)
* kill Coyotes (Loot Items)
* Finish Quests
* Turn in Quests Buzzard Wings
* be lvl 41 otherwise GRIND! 
* Port to Grom'Gol!
steps.tips: DO NOT SELL WINGS!

steps.description:
* Move Up to Duskwood
* at the end Go to the broken tower, Accept quest (turn in + next part)
* move to the Deadwind Pass

* start working on DREAM DUST (if all mobs down, go north)
* go north, into the cave, kill BIG MOB, loot Quest Item.
* go south and finish DREAM DUST quest.
* Look for Noboru the Cudgel ( /tar nob ), he drops a GREY weapon (starts a QUEST)
* Turn in Quest and accept "other quest" (no exclamation mark)
* Go South East

* Go to the in BIND YOURSELF to Stonard
* Accept the 2 Quests From Dar
* Go into the Big Building (Upstairs), Turn in Quest + Accept Pool of Tears
* leave EastWays

* Kill Crocodiles (Loot Item)
* Kill Tangled Horror (Loot Item)
* Kill Panther (Loot Item)
* Swim and loot Artifacts. (BLUE; DIVE)
* Go South East TO the Misty Post

* Kill Sawtooth Snapper (Loot Items), Fight your way North
* In the Cage, Escort Human.
* Kill ONGEKU (LOOT ITEM!)!
* On the way Kill mobs and Loot Crystals
* Turn in Quest on a Black Chest near a destroyed Tent
* Go NorthWest

* Turn In Quest
* go to Stoneard turn in quest, The Atal'ai Exile
* Go East to the Misty Reed Post

* Kill All Murlocs and Monstrous Crawlers (Loot Items, Crawler Leg)
* Turn In Quest. SKIP: Continued Threat for now
* HS BACK TO STONARD
* turn in Quest
* Fly to Booty Bay
steps.tips: * you should be 42 by now

steps.description:
* Accept: The Bloodsail Buccaneers, Skullsplitter Tusks
* Turn in Quest, Accept: Up to Snuff
* on the first Floor accept: Venture Company Mining, Zanzil's Secret
* BIND YOURSELF in BOOTY BAY (HS)
* in front of the bank: Akiris by the Bundle
* in the Cabin near the shark: Vodoo dues
* near the Exit (npc: Dizzy One-Eye): Keep An Eye Out
* leave Booty Bay
steps.tips: * if Quest log is full - abort Desolance quest (not: Ongeku) + Parts of the Swarm

steps.description:
* Kill Bloodsails, Loot Eye, Snuff, go to the Tend At the WEST, on 2 barrels are 2 Papers, use it
* Go North West to the Naga

* Kill Naga, Loot Akiris Reed the Nagas
* go Up the Hill until you reach the holy Spring
* if u killed all naga + have all Reed leave north ways.

* Look for Tethis, Kill and Loot
* go back (South East)

* Kill Zombies, Loot Items
* kill the 3 named Mobs (2 on the Street, 1 on the Beach) (loot Items)
* go north, Kill Goblin, loot Crystals
* Go north.

* Kill Trolls until both quests are Complete,
* aka: Spirit Bone Necklace, SkullSplinter Tusk
* Go north to the Nesingwary's Expedition.
* Turn in all Quests, Accept: Big Game Hunter
* Go South to Grom'Gol

* Turn in Quest
* Accept Grim Message + Marg Speaks (Cooking Pot)
* Kill Elite Crocodile until Quest Item Drops
* go south to kill Bangalash
steps.tips:
* Also these elites spawn by killing the regular Saltwater Crocolisks, 
* so you may need to kill some of them first to get the elites to spawn in

steps.description:
* Kill King Bangalash (lvl 43 Elite at 38, 35)
* go north to the Nesingwary's Expedition Turn in Quest
* Hearthstone to Booty Bay

* Turn IN ALL Quests
* Accept only: Rumors for Kravel, Tran'rek, Stoley's Debt
* go on the Board to Ratchet.
* in Ratchet fly to Brackenwall Village, Dustwallow Marsh

* Accept all Quests
* Go south to kill Deadmire 
* Go East to the crashed zeppelin

* Kill Muckshells until Quest Item Drop.
* Go southeast into the Elite Area.

* fight trough the elite mobs, Kill Scout, Ash Tail, Scalebane (in the Tunnel)
* Loot Mok'Morokks Stuff (Strongbox is in the Tunnel)
* Kill Welplings ( RED W ) until quest Complete. 
* if you lvl 43 @ ~85% Exp. Grind Back to the Brackenwall Village.
steps.tips: * you must grind some mobs at this point.

steps.description:
* Turn in Quests
* Accept Onyxia next part quest, until u must destroy 5 Eggs. (Skip this one for now)
* Fly to ThunderBluff.

* Go to the Hunters Rise, Turn in Quests
* If you have wool / Silk / Mageweave (x60) turn it in 
* Fly to Shadowprey Village, Desolace
steps.tips: * Visit your Class trainer if u want

steps.description:
* Bind yourself HERE (HS)
* the Tauren next to the GONG has a quest Accept it (No indicator!, just talk)
* leave the Village

* Accept Kolkar Quest, 
* Accept Goblin Quest (No Indicator, Just TALK)
* go into the Camp, and accept The Corrupter

* Look For the Deepstrider Giant, Kill And Loot (39 Elite)
* Go South

* Kill Boss Kolkar Khan
* Move South
* Place Ghost magnet on the Ground by the Skeletons (BLUE)
* move north west.
* Look for "LORD Azrethoc" Patrols in the blue (BLUE) (use: /tar Lord )
* Use Portals, Kill the Spawning Demons from the Portals
* Kill Jugkar Grim'rod (RED CIRCLE)
* Go North

* Turn in all QUEST
* don't accept new (Khan Hratha)
* HS BACK
* Turn in Quest
* Fly to Gadgetzan, Tanaris

* Enter Gadgetzan
* turn in "Tran'Rek", SKIP "Scarab Shells"
* Poster, BIG CAGE Accept, "WANTED: Caliph Scorpidsting" and "WANTED: Andre Firebeard"
* Bind yourself in Gadgetzan (HS)
* at the little tower accept, "Water Pouch Bounty" and "Wastewander Justice"
* Gadgetzan Water Survey at the west Hill
* Go Shimmering Flats

* Turn in Quests
* accept: Back to Booty Bay, Safety First, Keeping Pace
* BLUE Quest Mark, END QUEST, go to the WEST HUT, on the ground click on the Plans
* go back to the Goblins Turn in the BLUE QUEST.
* HS Back to Gadgetzan
* DESTORY, Sample of Indurium Ore
* Turn IN QUEST on the West side, SKIP next PART.
steps.tips: * If u had abort the Parts of the Swarm, reaccept it NOW, north west Shimmering Flats

steps.description:
* Grind your Way East
* Kill all Humans in the Ruins (KEEP THE Water Pouch), (do not finish yet)
* Go east, Accept ALL Quests.
* Go south West, Kill Humans, Grind a while here, very good spot!
* look for the Named use, ( /tar caliph ), Kill, Loot head
* Grund until you Reach lvl 45
* Go south on the Beach,
steps.tips: * Great AOE Bomb Place,

steps.description:
* Kill Everything, Loot Hats
* on the First building (Right), go upstairs Loot stolen Shipment
* If everything done, HS to Gadgetzan

* Turn in Quest, and turn in as many Water Pouches as you have, (KEEP 5 ON THE BANK!!!)
* accept "More Wastewander Justice"
* Go West until you reach the water pound, (avoid ELITE)
* use Untapped Dowsing Widget in the Pound.
* GO back to Gadgetzan, turn in Quest (don't accept next Part!)
* Go East ways until you reach the beach.

* Turn in Quest, Accept Deliver to MacKinley
* Go back to Gadgetzan, put on the bank: 
* Kravel's Scheme, Stoley's Bottle, Water Pouches, + if you found OOX-17/TN (do not accept!)
* Fly to Freewind Post (1K Needles)
* Fast Travel into Feralas, WEST!

* Run into Camp Mojache
* accept "A New Cloak's Sheen" + "The Ogres of Feralas" + "Gordunni Cobalt"
** "War on the Woodpaw" + "The Mark of Quality" + "A Strange Request"
* get Flight Point + Bind yourself in Mojache (HS)

* Kill Groll Mane (Loot Items)
* Kill Ogre
* use in the Orge Camp the Shovel (Blue Spots on the ground), loot Cobalt.
* next to the Big FirePlace, there is a scroll on the Ground (between stump and a Box, Loot!)
* accept Quest
* Everything finished? Go south West.

* Kill Sprite Darter, Loot Wings
* Go back to, Camp Mojache, Turn in Quests, 
* accept: "Alpha Strike" + "Dark Ceremony" + "The Ogres of Feralas" + "A Grim Discovery"
* Go South

* Kill 5 Woodpaw Alphas.
* Go back to Camp. Turn in Quest Accept next Part 
* Go Back to the camp on a wooden BOX is a Map, Loot (72, 56)
* leave north way to the gromhorns. (north is another camp)
* HS back to Camp, Turn in Quests

* turn in quest + accept next parts 
* accept: "Zukk'ash Infestation" and "Stinglasher"
* Go South,

* Kill Slitihs and loot Items (Stinglasher's Glands + 10 Zukk'ash Carapace)
* Kill Screechers (Red Flying snakes; BLUE DOTS) + use Bramble items + Talk with spirits
* Go South to the Ogre, Kill all Mobs + Kill Mage-Lord until Quest Orb drops.
* go to the Yeti, NorthWest Cave, kill until u have 10 yeti hide looted
* Turn in Quest, DO NOT START ESCORT QUEST YET!!!
* run back to Camp
steps.tips: * If you find the OOX-22/FE, Accept quest NOW.

steps.description:
* Turn in quests + Accept follow Quests
* Fly to Orgrimmar.

* GO to the Bank
* Withdraw silk if had any. 
* get Quest Items
* Go to the first quest (keep left (ramp UP)) Turn in, Jump down
* Go to the second quest, Turn in + accept ONLY Ripple Recovery.
* go the 3th Quest Turn in 2 Quest + Accept Betrayed.
* Go the Cleft of Shadow, turn in quest + accept next part
* go to The Valley of Wisdom, turn in quest, get a blue ring. 
* HS back to Feralas
steps.tips: * Buy Skills if u need!

steps.description:
* Turn in quest, at the troll, WAIT a few seconds, accept: 
** "Testing the Vessel" and "Natural Materials".
* Go into the Tent, accept "Improved Quality"
* GO West to the Faerie Dragon
* have all 6 Minerals? Go West

* Kill Hippogryphs; Loot quest Items (ALSO LOOT: Long Elegant Feathers!, don't sell it)
* at the cliffs Loot a Hippogryph Egg,
* South east (BLUE CIRCLE), kill elite ENT (tree), for quest Item 
* if everything done, Go north to the Yeti.
* Go North

* go north East
* Kill Rage Yeti Loot Quest Items
* HS back to Camp Mojache
* Turn in Quests
* fly to Splintertree Post, Ashenvale
steps.tips: * grind until u reach 93% of lvl 46

steps.description:
* Go after the Bridge, South and accept Quest (ALLIANCE BASE, becareful)
* Go north kill Undeads until complete.
* go north kill Satyr 
* Go north, Turn in Quest (Betrayed) (Don't accept anything!)
* get flight Point
* if finish, Go back south East, turn in quest.
* Move to UnderCITY
steps.tips: * if u don't can port to UC, run after the Satyr down, Turn in quest, and then get the Flight Point

steps.description:
* Go NE to the Magic Quarter and accept "Lines of Communication"
* Go around Apothecarium 
* accept 2 Quest "Seeping Corruption + "Errand for Apothecary Zinge"
* Turn in Quest, accept next part, Go back and turn this also in accept next part (Into the Field)
* Put in the Bank:  Field Testing Kit and Box of Empty Vials
* GET  Bundle of Atal'ai Artifacts + Nimboya's Pike
* Fly to Tarrens Mill + BIND YOURSELF IN TARRENS MILL
* GO into the Hinterlands

* Grind your way to the first Quest
* Kill as many Trained Razorbeaks or Wild Gryphons you can. NEED long Feather (at least 10)
* Turn in quest, Accept "A Sticky Situation"

* Go through the entire Zone,
* Accept ALL Quest in the Camp
* Except: the Wanted, Separation Anxiety, SnapJaws, Gammerita, Lard list his Lunch
* get the  flight point at the docks.

* Kill Wolfs (RED 1)
* Kill MOONKIN (USE item "Drum" to skin) (RED 2)
* Go into CAVE (BLUE CIRCLE) loot support Crates
* Kill trolls on the (BLUE DOTS), look for a bucket in one of the 5 Positions
* Kill Griphon (LOOT Feather) (RED 3)
* Kill Wolfes (RED 4)
* Kill Bloodelves, there are 3 Reports on the Ground, start follow quest (RED 5)
* Kill Trolls loot skulls if u have 20 use the Pike (item) in east CAMP (RED 6)
* on Troll Camps (RED 6) are little Bottles on the Table, accept quest
* AREA chicken quest item, is in the Pound (North, SMALL YELLOW DOT), don't start escort!
steps.tips: * if quest log is full on the Bottles/or escort quest, abort UC RED quest.

steps.description:
* Turn in Quest, accept next quest. 
* go to the Revantusk Village (East coast)

* Swim to the Island, use stone tablet / turn in accept new quest
* go into the camp, ONLY TURN IN QUESTS, do not accept any new quests!
* fly to Hammerfall if u need First Aid,
* Fly to Tarrens Mill
* Turn in Quest "Venom Bottles", accept "Undamaged Venom Sac"
* BIND YOURSELF in TARRENS MILL! (HS)
* WALK back into Hinterlands!

* Kill Spiders until venom sac drops
* Go up the South Pyramid, and Turn in quest (Jump down on the side)
* HS Back to Tarrens Mill
* Turn in Quest, SKIP Follow Quest.
* Fly To UnderCity

* From the BANK GET: Kravel's Scheme + Stoley's Bottle
* PUT: Dran's Ripple Delivery, 10 Wildkin Muisek, Wildkin Muisek Vessel
* Turn in Quests
* leave Undercity with the Zeppelin to Grom'Gol
* Fly to Booty Bay

* Accept ONLY The Bloodsail Buccaneers from the Tauren in the INN
* BIND YOURSELF in BOOTY BAY (HS)
* Turn in all quests
* Go up the Pier, accept "The Captains Chest" 
* Leave BootyBay

* Go on the Beach, Loot Bottles in the sand (sometimes under water) (BLUE DOT)
* kill Giant, (RED CIRCLE)
* if u have found the QUEST letter in a bottle accept, go to the island in the east, turn in quest
* accept next one, Kill Elite APE, Go back turn in quest
* to to the pirates ships in the west, Kill Captain (under deck!)
* in every ship can be a scroll on the ground, look for it, LOOT and accept.
* HS back to Booty bay
steps.tips: * after accepting the riddle scroll, item can be destroyed.

steps.description:
* Turn in 2 Quests,
* go to the bank GET: Mire Lord Fungus, 5 Shadow Panther Heart, Deepstrider Tumor, 15 Silk
* fly to Kargath, Badlands

* TO to the Searing Gorge
* go up the Mountain until u reach a little toilet house, accept quest!

* Kill Geologist + gather 15 silk cloth,
* turn in quest, accept next part
* Kill Spiders (RED DOTS) loot quest items
* if all spider legs looted go northWEST

* Accept quest "Divine Retribution", Just Talk to him again, Turn in quest, accept next part
* Go to the Thorium Point, get Flight path
* ACCPET ALL QUEST (WANTED BOARD Too) should be 7 in total!

* Kill every Golem / Elemental you see! (The Flawless Flame / Curse These Fat Fingers) (RED E)
* Kill Lava Spiders (RED SP)
* kill mobs: Smithing Tuyere + Lookout's Spyglass, can be found by (RED S) + (RED L) 
* Kill dark iron Dark Iron dwarves
steps.tips: * a key can drop from the Dark Iron dwarves, accept quest.

steps.description:
* Jump Down into the Cave.
* Kill dark Iron in the cave, on the Left, after the Bridge, there is a named "Maltorius", kill / loot
* behind him Loot Plans.
* Jump down behind the entrance if u have all Dark Iron dwarves
* Kill 20 Incendosaurs
* leave cave and canyon, go west side
steps.tips: * Save every Dark Iron Scraps

steps.description:
* Turn in Quests,
* Kill Elite Mobs West, Loot Symbol of Ragnaros
* turn in Ragnaros Quest, WAIT A FEW SECONDS!
* turn in, loot Staff Floating in mid-air and turn in again, until u have "Set Them Ablaze

* Set little fire pits on top of the 4 Tower on fire, (very little)
* GO with the KEY to the toilet in the east, free the Dwarf, Loot the book on the Ground!
* go back to Windblade (turn in quest)
* LOOT chest on the ground!, loot chest again Turn in quest, Loot chest in inventory
* (KEEP BLACK Dragonflight Molt!) 
* Go south in the Burning Steps, Trough Blackrock

* Get the Discovery Exp, 
* die at the Elite mobs, Res at ghost healer, move up the Ramp get Flight point
* go to Stonard, Swamp of Sorrows

* make stonard your new home.
* Go South, Speak with GhostOrc, Accept / turn in Quest, Accept next part
* go northWest UNDER the bridge in the water, is a scroll use it, Turn in quest, accept next part
* if "Nothing but the Truth" is ray, go East to Duskwood and Turn in. 
* HS back to Stonard (if rdy)
* go back to Stoneard Turn in Quests, Accept ONLY "The Missing Orders"
* Turn in Quest in the INN / accept next part
* Go East

* Go east and accept "Continued Thread", 
* Go west into the cave, kill all mobs, complete quest
* go back and turn in quest.
* Go to the beach, kill Jarquia loot quest Item.
* Die, and Rezz at Stonard!

* Turn in quest, Accept next part, Talk with him.
* turn in quest / SKIP NEXT PART
* go back to Stonard, fly to booty Bay
* Accept Quest in the INN (Wiskey Slims Log Grog, from a Gnome)
* Go To Ratchet
steps.tips:
* PUT BANK  Goodsteel Ledger, 20 Solid Crystal Leg Shafts, 
* Goodsteel's Balanced Flameberge, Torch of Retribution, Black Dragonflight Molt, 
* Dark Iron Scraps and any Core of Elements.
* GET  10 Wildkin Muisek, Wildkin Muisek Vessel

steps.description:
* Accept The Brood of Onyxia (Cave),
* go south to crashed Zeppelin, Loot Damaged Crate.
* Go south Destroy Eggs.
* go West into a small Cave (Raptors), there is a Riddle Scroll in it. Turn in / Accept it
* Go back to the Village. Turn in Quest.
* Speak with Overloard Mok, accept quest and beat him in a fight. / turn in quest
* Fly to Camp Mojache, Feralas

* Turn in / Accept ALL Quests
* BIND YOURSELF IN FERALAS  (HS)
* Go West. do Hippogryph Muisek

* go Southwest to the Hippogryphs, kill and use Quest Item.
* Port back and turn in quest / accept next part.
* go to the Faery Dragons, kill, Use item, 
* Go back and turn in / accept next part.

* Swap from north to south until zu kill all Treants (Use Quest Item)
* Turn in Quest  / accept next part
* Go West way.

* Accept all quests from the Goblin.
* Go north, and kill Water Elementals / Loot Item
* use Quest Item on Giants to shrink, Kill Zapped Giant; loot item
* go back to Goblin, (Skip FOLLOW quest, its the same but not much Exp!)
* Accept anyway Zapped Giants! Go north
* Use the Zapper at the Giants, Then Kill, Then use the Muisek Vessel, until finished
* go north kill harpies, go far north between 2 big stones, use HORN, Kill elite.
* Go back to Goblin turn in, HS back to Camp Mojache Turn in quests,
* Fly to Gadgetzan, Tanaris

* Bind yourself in Gadgetzan (HS)
* Accept Quests (do not accept Dungeon Quests.)
* get from the Bank: Yeh'kinya's Bramble, Goodsteel Ledger, 20 Solid Crystal Leg Shafts, 
** Goodsteel's Balanced Flameberge + Water Pouches + Hippogryph Egg.
* Go to the Egg Machine, Turn in Egg,, Loot Container, Speak to Gnome, Turn in Quest.+
* go to forge, turn in quest
* Leave South way

* Go South, Turn in Quest, Accept next part + Other quests
* go south west

* Kill Orge, Go into Cave Kill Named
* GO West to the Silithid area
steps.tips: * Loot Gahz'ridian btw. (equip Gahz'ridian Detector)

steps.description:
* Kill Silitith, until you find all parts. 
* Go south Kill Gnarled Thistleshrubs + 8 Thistleshrub Rootshapers, 
* loot Collectors for quest item (low drop chance)
* after complete, find Tooga, accept escort quest.
* go North east straight trough the ZONE (66.25)

* Turn in Quest, SKIP: The Prophecy of Mosh'aru
* Accept quest in the south Hut. 
* Hearthstone back to Gadgetzan

* Turn in Quests
* accept new Quests: In Good Taste, turn it in NW Gz
* accept: Sprinkle's Secret Ingredient + on the hill: The Scrimshank Redemption
* BANK GET: Field Testing Kit + OOX-17/TN Distress Beacon
* accept ITEM: Model 4711-FTZ Power Source

* Grind your way, LOOT hyena, scropids + crocodile samples (check the sample!)
* go to the Silithid area south, do the CHICKEN quest.

* turn in CHICKEN QUEST, escort quest need 21 Minutes... skip dat shit
* Make sure "Tanaris Field Sampling" is complete
* go into the NORTH cave, and keep Right.
* Loot item, Die on Purpose, Rez @ Gadgetzan
* Turn in All QUEST 
 *GET BANK: Box of Empty Vials
* Fly to OG, BIND URSELF in OG, Fly to Valormok, Azshara
steps.tips: Make sure you are level 50 otherwise GRIND!
